# TaskContext imports

`TaskProvider.jsx` exports **`TaskContext`** as a **named** export and **`TaskProvider`** as the **default** export.

```javascript
// BAD — default is the Provider component, not the context; useContext(...) is undefined
import TaskContext from "../../TaskState/TaskProvider.jsx";

// GOOD — same object passed to <TaskContext.Provider>
import { TaskContext } from "../../TaskState/TaskProvider.jsx";
```

Always destructure from `useContext(TaskContext)` after using the named import.
